[[File:EmperorKatarn.jpg|thumb|right|Emperor Katarn orders the extinction of the uprising.]]
{{Quote|I have no time for petty uprisings. Extinguish them&hellip;painfully.|Kyle Katarn|<ref name="Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II">''[[Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II]]''</ref>}}
Shortly after [[Kyle Katarn]] assumed the power of the [[Valley of the Jedi]] and became [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Galactic Emperor]] around [[5 ABY/Legends|5 ABY]], the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] initiated an '''uprising''' against him on [[Danuta]]. Emperor Katarn sent [[Sariss]] to crush the rebellion.

==Behind the scenes==
The uprising is mentioned only in the non-[[canon]] dark side alternative ending of the game ''Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II''.

